              "value": "=**From:** {{ $json.senderEmail }}\n**Subject:** {{ $json.emailSubject }}\n**AI Confidence:** {{ $json.aiConfidence }}%\n**Reason:** {{ $json.aiReason }}\n\n**Action Required:** Please manually review this email and create a ticket if needed."
            },
